    <h1>Brand Mentions</h1>
    <p class="description">Online references to a brand — linked or unlinked — across articles, forums, reviews, podcasts, and AI answers. In aggregate they act as <strong>entity-authority signals</strong> for Google and <strong>citation signals</strong> for AI Overviews.</p>
